{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n<body><p>更新時間：08:40 2026-04-30 HKT<br/>發佈時間：08:31 2026-04-30 HKT</p>\n<p>發佈時間：08:31 2026-04-30 HKT</p><p>大埔有人遇溺死亡。今日（30日）早上7時25分，汀角路168號龍尾泳灘對開約100米海面，有人在水中載浮載沉。救援人員趕到將事主救起，發現是一名七旬男子，但他已昏迷不醒，由救護車送往大埔那打素醫院，最終不治。</p><p>警方經調查後，證實死者是73歲姓劉老翁。據了解，事主是退休人士，有晨泳習慣，相信他游泳時遇溺。</p><img alt=\"現場是龍尾灘對開海面。蔡楚輝攝\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/ul/sthl/84029b559eee7673e63d979648313e2d/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260430_081132136_01.jpg\"/><img alt=\"警員調查事件。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/ul/sthl/e445c577b64f67f89de1e90bd9414c79/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260430_081132136_02.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/ul/sthl/10678cf8453ec5d69ac318ccf2e7e11b/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260430_081132136_03.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/ul/sthl/fdca01d20510bef0862cbd84478d5eb2/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260430_081132136_05.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/ul/sthl/35cc9ffecae32ff89b18a8e9d4572204/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260430_081132136_06.jpg\"/><img alt=\"男泳客在龍尾灘對開約100米海面漂浮，昏迷送院救治。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/ul/sthl/56ad12aa6bda148b134f3d8b1b91f5b8/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260430_081132136_07.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/ul/sthl/27378733e315f38d1094568578052a23/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260430_081132136_08.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/ul/sthl/2019b4fc19d742619f72dc7e3f00ee64/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260430_081132136_10.jpg\"/><p>最Hit</p>\n</body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-30T05:46:14.615411+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":235,"images":8,"source":"星島頭條","fallback":"none"}}